        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are generating an internal weekly TDX summary for the Emerging Technologies team.\n\nAnalyze the ticket data and provide a concise, readable weekly report.\n\nCRITICAL FORMATTING RULES:\n- Put each section on a NEW LINE\n- Insert a blank line between sections\n- Every bullet must start on its own line\n- Never place content on the same line as a heading\n- Never write one continuous paragraph\n\nGoals:\n- Identify recurring themes\n- Highlight major problems or friction points\n- Flag unresolved/unaddressed tickets\n- Surface important trends or operational concerns\n- Do NOT summarize every ticket individually\n- Include the full TeamDynamix ticket URL for every ticket listed under Unaddressed / Needs Attention\n\nTickets:\n{{\n$json.data.map(ticket => `\nTicket ID: ${ticket[\"Ticket ID\"]}\nTicket URL: https://teamdynamix.umich.edu/TDNext/Apps/31/Tickets/TicketDet.aspx?TicketID=$json.[\"Ticket ID\"]\nTitle: ${ticket.Title}\nDepartment: ${ticket[\"User Department\"]}\nStatus: $json.[\"Ticket Status\"]\nDescription: ${ticket.Description}\nComments: ${ticket.Comments}\n`).join('\\n\\n---\\n\\n')\n}}\nTotal Tickets: {{ $json[\"Total Tickets\"] }}\nClosed Tickets: {{ $json[\"Closed Tickets\"] }}\nOpen Tickets: {{ $json[\"Open Tickets\"] }}\nOutput EXACTLY as valid HTML suitable for an email.\n\nUse this structure:\n\n<h2>Weekly Summary</h2>\n<p>[3-5 sentence summary]</p>\n\n<h2>Major Themes</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Theme 1</li>\n  <li>Theme 2</li>\n  <li>Theme 3</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Ticket Counts</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Number of Total Tickets:</strong> [total number]</li>\n  <li><strong>Number of Open Tickets:</strong> [open ticket count]</li>\n  <li><strong>Number of Closed Tickets:</strong> [closed ticket count]</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Key Problems / Friction</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Problem 1</li>\n  <li>Problem 2</li>\n  <li>Problem 3</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Unaddressed / Needs Attention</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Ticket title (Ticket ID):</strong> <a href=\"ticket URL\">ticket URL</a> — issue or reason it needs attention</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Recommended Attention Areas</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recommendation 1</li>\n  <li>Recommendation 2</li>\n</ul>\n\nIf no tickets need attention, write:\n<h2>Unaddressed / Needs Attention</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>None identified</li>\n</ul>\n\nDo not use markdown. Return only HTML. Do not wrap the response in code block"
            }
          ]
        },
