      "parameters": {
        "content": "## This Template Demonstrates\nA workflow designed to read TDX Tickets and generate a summary of them to be emailed.\n- Scheduled weekly trigger\n- Gathers all tickets in the specific TDX ticket report\n- Filters the report for tickets from the last week\n- Gets the information from each ticket\n- Simultaneously gets the comments from each ticket\n- Merges the ticket and comment data\n- Sends the ticket data to an AI model to generate a summary\n- Sends the generated summary in an email\n\n",
        "height": 384,
        "width": 608,
        "color": 2
